-intern-doctor-at-svims-in-tirupati%2Farticleshow%2F112833996.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20outstation%20patient%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20Sri%20Venkateswara%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(SVIMS)%20in%20Tirupati%20attacked%20a%20female%20intern%20doctor.%20The%20patient%2C%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20conversion%20disorder%2C%20became%20aggressive%20and%20assaulted%20the%20doctor%20before%20collapsing%20again.%20This%20incident%20has%20reignited%20protests%20among%20resident%20doctors%20who%20demand%20enhanced%20security%20measures%20at%20the%20hospital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SANDEEP%20RAGHAVAN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvijayawada%2Fandhra-pradesh-patient-suffering-from-conversion-disorder-attacks-a-female-intern-doctor-at-svims-in-tirupati%2Farticleshow%2F112833996.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Teen%20Girls%20Found%20Hanging%20In%20UP%20Village%2C%20Family%20Alleges%20Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20girls%2C%20aged%2015%20and%2018%2C%20were%20found%20hanging%20dead%20from%20a%20tree%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Farrukhabad%20today.%20Family%20members%20have%20said%20the%20teenagers%20went%20to%20attend%20a%20Janmashtami%20programme%20last%20evening%2C%20but%20did%20not%20return.%20This%20morning%2C%20their%20bodies%20were%20found%20in%20a%20mango%20orchard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20recovered%20a%20phone%20from%20the%20spot%20and%20also%20found%20a%20SIM%20card%20on%20one%20of%20the%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20one%20of%20the%20girls%20said%20they%20had%20gone%20to%20attend%20a%20programme%20at%20the%20nearly%20temple%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Janmashtami.%20%26quot%3BThey%20went%20in%20the%20evening%20and%20returned%20around%209%20pm%20because%20it%20had%20started%20raining.%20Later%2C%20in%20the%20night%2C%20they%20went%20again.%20The%20programme%20ended%20around%201%20am.%20When%20they%20did%20not%20return%2C%20we%20started%20looking%20for%20them.%20A%20child%20said%20they%20slept%20at%20their%20aunt's%20place.%20We%20went%20there%2C%20but%20did%20not%20find%20them.%20Many%20of%20our%20relatives%20stay%20there%2C%20so%20we%20thought%20they%20must%20have%20slept%20there%20and%20will%20return%20in%20the%20morning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20morning%2C%20he%20said%2C%20one%20of%20their%20acquaintances%20informed%20that%20someone%20is%20hanging%20from%20a%20tree%20in%20the%20orchard.%20%26quot%3BAround%206%20am%2C%20we%20reached%20here%20and%20found%20the%20girls%20hanging.%20We%20think%20someone%20killed%20them%20and%20hanged%20them%20bodies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChilling%20visuals%20showed%20the%20girls%20hanging%20dead%20with%20two%20dupattas%20tied%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20police%20chief%20Alok%20Priyadarshi%20said%20the%20two%20girls%20were%20close%20friends.%20%26quot%3BThe%20autopsy%20will%20reveal%20details%20about%20the%20case.%20We%20have%20found%20a%20phone%20and%20a%20SIM%20card.%20We%20are%20using%20them%20to%20gather%20information%20and%20speaking%20to%20the%20family%20members.%20The%20matter%20will%20be%20investigated%20in%20detail%20and%20action%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20have%20been%20sent%20for%20autopsy%20and%20a%20forensic%20team%20collected%20evidence%20from%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20leader%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20main%20Opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20has%20demanded%20swift%20investigation%20and%20said%20such%20incidents%20create%20an%20environment%20of%20fear%20in%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20incident%20sensitive%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20government%20should%20immediately%20conduct%20a%20fair%20investigation%20and%20clear%20the%20air%20on%20this%20suspected%20case%20of%20murder.%20Such%20incidents%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20in%20the%20society%20and%20deeply%20hurt%20the%20women%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20time%20to%20rise%20above%20politics%20and%20treat%20women's%20safety%20as%20a%20serious%20issue%20has%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724751240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Foo2uh83g_farrukhabad-teen-deaths_625x300_27_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarrukhabad-2-teen-girls-found-hanging-in-up-village-family-alleges-murder-6428325%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20girls%2C%20aged%2015%20and%2018%2C%20were%20found%20hanging%20dead%20from%20a%20tree%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Farrukhabad%20today.%20Family%20members%20have%20said%20the%20teenagers%20went%20to%20attend%20a%20Janmashtami%20programme%20last%20evening%2C%20but%20did%20not%20return.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20Does%20BJP%20Want%20A%20Change%20In%20Polling%20Date%20In%20Haryana%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F3vn1d678_haryana_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20(BJP)%20state%20unit%20has%20requested%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20to%20change%20the%20polling%20date%20in%20Haryana%2C%20citing%20concerns%20that%20a%20long%20weekend%20could%20affect%20voter%20turnout.%20The%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20fearing%20a%20loss%20and%20using%20the%20request%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20delay%20the%20election.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20asserted%20its%20readiness%20for%20elections%20on%20any%20date.%20The%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%20has%20also%20supported%20the%20BJP's%20demand%20for%20a%20date%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI's%20state%20unit%20has%20forwarded%20the%20application%20to%20Delhi%20and%20is%20awaiting%20a%20response.%20Haryana%20is%20scheduled%20to%20vote%20on%20October%201%20(Tuesday)%2C%20along%20with%20the%20third%20and%20final%20phase%20of%20voting%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20with%20results%20to%20be%20announced%20on%20October%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong%20Weekends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20September%2028-29%20are%20weekends%20and%20October%202-3%20are%20holidays%20(for%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20Jayanti%20and%20Maharaja%20Agrasen%20Jayanti)%2C%20a%20person%20who%20takes%20leave%20on%20September%2030%20could%20enjoy%20a%20six-day%20break%2C%20including%20polling%20day%2C%20which%20is%20also%20a%20public%20holiday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana's%20urbanisation%20level%20was%2028.9%25%20according%20to%20the%202011%20census%2C%20a%20figure%20likely%20to%20have%20increased%20with%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR).%20Fourteen%20districts%20of%20Haryana%20are%20part%20of%20the%20NCR%2C%20including%20key%20urban%20centres%20such%20as%20Gurugram%2C%20Faridabad%2C%20Rohtak%2C%20Sonipat%20and%20Bhiwani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20traditionally%20performs%20well%20in%20urban%20areas.%20Some%20of%20these%20cities%20also%20have%20a%20high%20migrant%20population%2C%20which%20might%20use%20the%20extended%20break%20to%20visit%20their%20homes%2C%20potentially%20affecting%20the%20BJP's%20performance.%20Historically%2C%20rural%20turnout%20has%20been%20higher%20than%20urban%20turnout%20in%20general%20elections%2C%20though%20the%20gap%20has%20varied%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20rural%20turnout%20was%2067.9%25%20compared%20to%2057.9%25%20in%20urban%20areas.%20While%20rural%20turnout%20fell%20by%20around%203%20percentage%20points%20from%202019%2C%20urban%20turnout%20dropped%20by%20approximately%207%20percentage%20points.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20turnout%20fluctuated%20during%20four%20weekend%20phases%2C%20with%20an%20increase%20seen%20in%20two%20phases%20and%20decline%20in%20the%20other%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETurnout%20Concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20acknowledges%20that%20lower%20turnout%20negatively%20impacted%20its%20performance%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%20The%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20among%20key%20leaders%2C%20workers%2C%20and%20supporters%20contributed%20to%20the%20party%20falling%20short%20of%20a%20majority%2C%20as%20noted%20in%20the%20internal%20UP%20poll%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20high%20turnout%20is%20crucial%20for%20the%20BJP's%20success.%20From%201996%20to%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20formed%20the%20central%20government%20five%20times%2C%20with%20increased%20turnout%20in%20four%20of%20these%20instances.%20Despite%20boasting%20the%20title%20of%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20world%20and%20having%20a%20network%20of%20panna%20pramukhs%20(each%20managing%2030%20voters)%2C%20the%20BJP%20apprehends%20that%20if%20some%20voters%20opt%20for%20vacation%20instead%20of%20voting%2C%20this%20advantage%20could%20be%20diminished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20BJP's%20demand%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20dismissed%20the%20concerns%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20nervousness.%20Deepender%20Hooda%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20that%20the%20BJP's%20request%20for%20a%20date%20change%20is%20an%20excuse%20to%20delay%20the%20elections%2C%20reflecting%20its%20lack%20of%20substantive%20issues%2C%20achievements%2C%20or%20candidates%20for%20all%2090%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELimited%20Scope%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20requested%20a%20deferral%20of%20the%20elections%2C%20proposing%20a%20change%20in%20dates%20or%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20polling%20period.%20With%20October%202%20and%20October%203%20being%20holidays%20and%20October%204%20reserved%20for%20results%2C%20the%20entire%20polling%20process%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Haryana%20must%20be%20completed%20by%20October%206.%20There%20is%20limited%20scope%20for%20postponing%20the%20polls%3B%20if%20the%20ECI%20considers%20a%20change%2C%20it%20might%20have%20to%20advance%20the%20date%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20would%20likely%20oppose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20is%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20highly%20polarised%2C%20with%20Jats%2C%20a%20dominant%20social%20group%20in%20the%20state%2C%20supporting%20the%20Congress%20and%20non-Jats%20backing%20the%20BJP.%20In%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20all%20five%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20non-Jat%20dominated%20areas.%20The%20party%20is%20strong%20in%20urban%20regions%20like%20Faridabad%2C%20Ambala%2C%20and%20Gurugram%2C%20winning%2022%20of%20its%2040%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUrban-Rural%20Divide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20concern%20is%20that%20some%20voters%20may%20use%20the%20extended%20weekends%20for%20vacations%2C%20which%20could%20impact%20turnout.%20This%20situation%20highlights%20the%20growing%20inequality%20between%20urban%20and%20rural%20India%2C%20as%20urban%20voters%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20afford%20vacations%20compared%20to%20their%20rural%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Haryana%2C%20Jats%2C%20who%20are%20predominantly%20farmers%2C%20have%20been%20disillusioned%20by%20the%20Centre's%20response%20to%20their%20protests.%20The%20Congress%20is%20working%20to%20consolidate%20a%20Jat-Dalit-Muslim%20alliance%20in%20rural%20areas.%20The%20BJP's%20loss%20of%20five%20out%20of%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%202024%20compared%20to%202019%20suggests%20it%20is%20on%20the%20defensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20led%20in%2044%20assembly%20segments%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20led%20in%2042%2C%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20four.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20led%20in%2079%20seats%20but%20won%20only%2040%20in%20the%20subsequent%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20polls%20held%20six%20months%20later.%20As%20the%20party%20faces%20ten%20years%20of%20incumbency%2C%20it%20aims%20to%20address%20all%20potential%20issues%2C%20including%20the%20election%20date%2C%20to%20secure%20a%20favourable%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20ECI%20will%20accommodate%20this%20request%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724751120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F3vn1d678_haryana_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-does-bjp-want-a-change-in-polling-date-in-haryana-6428312%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP's%20concern%20is%20that%20some%20voters%20may%20use%20the%20extended%20weekends%20for%20vacations%2C%20which%20could%20impact%20turnout.%20This%20situation%20highlights%20the%20growing%20inequality%20between%20urban%20and%20rural%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Reiterated%20India's%20commitment%20to...'%3A%20PM%20Modi%20speaks%20to%20Putin%20after%20Ukraine%20visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724750596000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112833825%2Cimgsize-1110646.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Freiterated-indias-firm-commitment-to-pm-modi-speaks-to