com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc2048rnqxego.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20Will%20Help%20Replace%20Non-Performing%20Pak%20Cricketers.%20Yes%2C%20It%20Is%20Happening%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeeing%20Pakistan's%20cricketing%20performance%20chart%20going%20down%20with%20every%20passing%20series%2C%20the%20country's%20board%20has%20opted%20for%20a%20unique%20approach%20to%20finding%20talent.%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20chief%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20selection%20of%20players%20from%20the%20country's%20domestic%20spectrum%20is%20broadly%20being%20done%20using%20artificial%20intelligence.%20While%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20is%20gaining%20prominence%20in%20the%20field%20of%20Information%20Technology%2C%20E-Commerce%2C%20and%20several%20other%20businesses%2C%20the%20PCB%20has%20become%20the%20first%20board%20to%20openly%20reveal%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20their%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Naqvi%20spoke%20to%20the%20media%20about%20the%20under-par%20performances%20of%20the%20men's%20national%20team%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20recent%20defeat%20against%20Bangladesh%20at%20home.%20Naqvi%20had%20famously%20called%20for%20a%20need%20to%20do%20surgery%20after%20Pakistan's%20early%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20exit%2C%20but%20not%20much%20has%20changed%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20the%20selection%20committee%20has%20no%20pool%20to%20turn%20to%20from%20which%20to%20select%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PCB%20chairman%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20spoke%20of%20surgery%20because%20we%20need%20to%20fix%20our%20problems.%20But%20when%20we%20look%20at%20how%20to%20resolve%20them%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20any%20solid%20data%20or%20player%20pool%20which%20we%20can%20draw%20from.%20The%20whole%20system%20was%20a%20mess.%20The%20Champions%20Cup%20will%20produce%20great%20talent%2C%20and%20we'll%20have%20records%20for%20the%20games%20that%20happen.%20For%20surgery%2C%20you%20need%20all%20the%20tools%20to%20perform%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20players%20for%20which%20we%20didn't%20have%20records.%20This%20Cup%20will%20make%20domestic%20cricket%20strong%2C%20we'll%20have%20a%20pool%20of%20150%20players%2C%20and%20then%20the%20surgery%20we%20need%20to%20be%20done%2C%20the%20selection%20committee%20will%20do.%20People%20said%20'do%20it%20all%20today%2C%20slit%20the%20throats%20of%20four-five%20players%2C%20and%20get%20rid%20of%20them'.%20You%20can't%20dump%20someone%20unless%20you%20have%20a%20better%20one%20to%20replace%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Naqvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaqvi%20revealed%20that%20the%20150%20players%20who%20will%20be%20selected%2C%20will%20see%2080%25%20population%20getting%20picked%20purely%20using%20AI.%20The%20human%20involvement%20will%20be%20just%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20150%20players%20that%20have%20been%20selected%2C%2080%25%20of%20it%20has%20been%20done%20by%20AI%20(Artificial%20intelligence)%2C%20and%2020%25%20using%20humans.%20Nobody%20can%20challenge%20that.%20We%20gave%20about%2020%25%20weightage%20to%20our%20selection%20committee.%20If%20we%20replace%20a%20player%20with%20a%20worse%20one%2C%20you'll%20be%20the%20first%20to%20complain.%20We'll%20have%20records%20and%20we'll%20all%20be%20able%20to%20see%20transparently%20who%20deserves%20a%20place%20in%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chairman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Champions%20Cup%20will%20end%20in%20September%2C%20and%20then%20there%20will%20be%20records%20for%20everyone.%20Anyone%20who%20isn't%20performing%20will%20be%20immediately%20replaced.%20It%20shouldn't%20come%20down%20to%20anyone's%20individual%20opinions%20and%20wishes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724748060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F86eguico_pak-team-x_625x300_27_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fai-will-help-pcb-replace-non-performing-pakistan-cricketers-yes-it-is-happening-6427619%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20has%20announced%20a%20unique%20AI-driven%20approach%20for%20selection%20of%20players.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fai-will-help-pcb-replace-non-performing-pakistan-cricketers-yes-it-is-happening-6427619%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20The%20Farakka%20Barrage%20Pact%20Amid%20'Fake%20News'%20On%20Bangladesh%20Floods%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20is%20facing%20devastating%20floods%20across%20the%20country%20caused%20by%20relentless%20monsoon%20rain%20and%20overflowing%20rivers.%20The%20death%20count%20from%20the%20floods%20has%20risen%20to%2023%2C%20and%20more%20than%2012.4%20lakh%20families%20are%20stranded%20across%2011%20districts%20in%20the%20country.%2057%20lakh%20people%20remain%20isolated%20and%20in%20urgent%20need%20of%20food%2C%20clean%20water%2C%20medicine%20and%20dry%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20times%2C%20reports%20in%20Bangladesh%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20flooding%20is%20caused%20partially%20due%20to%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Farakka%20barrage%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20prompting%20a%20fact-check%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20on%20Monday%20rejected%20all%20reports%20linking%20the%20floods%20in%20Bangladesh%20with%20the%20opening%20of%20Farakka%20barrage%20gates%20in%20India%2C%20calling%20such%20reports%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20fake%20videos%2C%20rumours%20and%20fear-mongering%20to%20create%20misunderstanding.%20This%20should%20be%20firmly%20countered%20with%20facts%2C%26quot%3B%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20relevant%20data%20is%20shared%20with%20joint%20river%20commission%20officials%20concerned%20in%20Bangladesh%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bregular%20and%20timely%20basis%2C%20and%20it%20was%20done%20this%20time%20as%20well%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20media%20reports%20of%20the%20opening%20of%20Farakka%20barrage%20gates%20that%20will%20allow%20the%20flow%20of%20over%2011%20lakh%20cusecs%20of%20water%20downstream%20of%20the%20river%20in%20its%20natural%20course%20into%20the%20Ganga%2FPadma%20river%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20normal%20seasonal%20development%20that%20takes%20place%20due%20to%20increased%20inflow%20from%20heavy%20rainfall%20in%20the%20Ganga%20river%20basin%20catchment%20areas%20upstream%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20in%20detail%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20to%20be%20understood%20that%20Farakka%20is%20only%20a%20barrage%20and%20not%20a%20dam.%20Whenever%20the%20water%20level%20reaches%20the%20pond%20level%2C%20whatever%20inflow%20comes%2C%20that%20passes.%20It%20is%20merely%20a%20structure%20to%20divert%2040%2C000%20cusecs%20of%20water%20into%20the%20Farakka%20canal%20that%20is%20carefully%20done%20using%20a%20system%20of%20gates%20on%20the%20main%20Ganga%2FPadma%20river%2C%20while%20the%20balance%20water%20flows%20into%20the%20main%20river%20to%20Bangladesh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20Farakka%20Barrage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Farakka%20Barrage%20is%20situated%20on%20the%20Ganga%20River%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Murshidabad%20district.%20It%20is%20located%20approximately%2018%20km%20from%20the%20border%20with%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20of%20the%20Farakka%20Barrage%20began%20in%201962%20and%20was%20completed%20in%201970%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20nearly%20USD%201%20billion.%20The%20barrage%20officially%20commenced%20operations%20on%20April%2021%2C%201975.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20purpose%20of%20the%20barrage%20is%20to%20merely%20divert%2040%2C000%20cusecs%20of%20water%20into%20the%20Farakka%20canal%20and%20is%20carefully%20done%20using%20a%20system%20of%20gates%20on%20the%20main%20Ganga%20river%2C%20while%20the%20balance%20water%20flows%20into%20the%20main%20river%20which%20then%20flows%20to%20Bangladesh%20in%20its%20natural%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Farakka%20Barrage%20Agreement%2C%201977%20And%20The%20Ganga%20Water%20Treaty%2C%201996%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ganga%20river%20flows%20from%20India%20into%20Bangladesh%2C%20where%20its%20primary%20distributary%20is%20known%20as%20the%20Padma%20river.%20The%20river%20ultimately%20drains%20into%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20after%20a%20confluence%20with%20the%20river%20Meghna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20India%20to%20establish%20the%20Farakka%20barrage%20was%20to%20flush%20out%20the%20silt%20of%20Bhagirathi%20Hoogly%20river%20to%20ensure%20smooth%20operation%20of%20Kolkata%20port.%20Bangladesh%20said%20that%20Ganga%20is%20an%20international%20river%2C%20so%20the%20water%20from%20it%20must%20be%20regulated%20as%20per%20a%20mutual%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20nations%2C%20in%201972%2C%20established%20a%20Joint%20River%20Commission%20(JRC)%20to%20negotiate%20terms%20of%20the%20water%20settlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangaldesh%20opposed%20India's%20suggestions%20and%20in%201977%2C%20the%20then%20President%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20Zia-Ur-Rehman%2C%20took%20the%20Farakka%20barrage%20issue%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20or%20UNGA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UNGA%20urged%20him%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20at%20a%20bilateral%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%201977%2C%20then%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20Babu%20Jagjivan%20Ram%20went%20on%20an%20official%20visit%20to%20Bangladesh%20and%20signed%20an%20agreement%20to%20resolve%20the%20Farrakka%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20Bangladesh's%20Awami%20League%20and%20the%20new%20government%20signed%20a%20fresh%20treaty%20with%20India%20-%20known%20as%20The%20Ganga%20Water%20Treaty%2C%201996.%20The%20agreement%20was%20to%20share%20the%20surface%20waters%20at%20the%20Farakka%20Barrage%20near%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlood-Prone%20Bangladesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20in%202015%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%20Institute%20estimated%20that%203.5%20million%20people%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20climate-vulnerable%20countries%2C%20were%20at%20risk%20of%20annual%20river%20flooding.%20Scientists%20attribute%20the%20exacerbation%20of%20such%20catastrophic%20events%20to%20climate%20change.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724747880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fq3dpekn_farakka-barrage-west-bengal_625x300_27_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-the-farakka-barrage-agreement-amid-fake-news-on-bangladesh-floods-6427801%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reports%20in%20Bangladesh%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20flooding%20in%20the%20country%20is%20caused%20partially%20due%20to%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Farakka%20barrage%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20prompting%20a%20fact-check%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20which%20trashed%20all%20such%20reports%20as%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-the-farakka-barrage-agreement-amid-fake-news-on-bangladesh-floods-6427801%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top-level%20meeting%20shows%20China%20-%20and%20Xi%20-%20still%20a%20priority%20for%20Biden%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724747729000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fcd00%2Fli