%20Cannons%2C%20Tear%20Gas%20On%20Protesters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChaotic%20scenes%20are%20being%20witnessed%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Kolkata%20as%20police%20intercepted%20a%20protest%20march%20to%20state%20secretariat%20Nabanna%20over%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20in%20the%20city's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20on%20August%209.%C2%A0Riot%20police%20are%20using%20teargas%20shells%20and%20water%20cannons%20to%20stop%20the%20protesters%20from%20proceedings%20towards%20the%20state%20secretariat.%20Some%20of%20the%20protesters%20are%20throwing%20stones%20towards%20the%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20permission%20was%20given%20for%20the%20protest%20march%20and%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20yesterday%20alleged%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20create%20unrest%20throw%20violence%20during%20the%20rally.%20Kolkata%20Police%20virtually%20turned%20Nabanna%20into%20a%20fortress%20and%20as%20many%20as%206%2C000%20police%20personnel%20were%20deployed%20to%20stop%20the%20protesters%20from%20advancing%20the%20secretariat%20from%20any%20route.%20Drones%20were%20also%20used%20to%20keep%20a%20watch%20on%20the%20protesters.%20Barricades%20have%20been%20welded%20into%20the%20ground%20and%20greased%20to%20prevent%20the%20protesters%20from%20scaling%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20a%20group%20of%20protesters%20gathered%20at%20College%20Square%20and%20marched%20towards%20Nabanna.%20They%20raised%20slogans%20demanding%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20resignation%20over%20the%20horrific%20rape%20and%20murder%20case.%20Several%20student%20organisations%20and%20citizen%20forums%20have%20joined%20the%20protest.%20Visuals%20showed%20the%20protesters%20shaking%20the%20barricades%20in%20their%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20alleges%20this%20is%20a%20BJP-backed%20protest%2C%20the%20organisers%20have%20said%20it%20is%20a%20march%20planned%20by%20student%20organisations.%20Many%20of%20the%20outfits%20part%20of%20today's%20protest%20are%20not%20registered%20organisations.%20Most%20known%20student%20outfits%2C%20including%20those%20affiliated%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20have%20distanced%20themselves%20from%20the%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Bengal%20Assembly%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20said%20four%20student%20activists%20part%20of%20the%20protest%20plan%20went%20missing%20after%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20following%20Student%20Activists%20who%20were%20distributing%20food%20to%20the%20volunteers%2C%20who%20were%20arriving%20at%20Howrah%20Station%2C%20suddenly%20went%20missing%20after%20midnight%20%3A-%20Subhojit%20Ghosh%2C%20Pulokesh%20Pandit%2C%20Goutam%20Senapati%2C%20Pritam%20Sarkar.%C2%A0Neither%20they%20can%20be%20traced%20nor%20are%20they%20answering%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20apprehend%20that%20they%20may%20have%20been%20arrested%2Fdetained%20by%20the%20Mamata%20Police.%20If%20something%20happens%20to%20them%20Mamata%20Police%20will%20be%20held%20accountable%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adhikari%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20police%20responded%20that%20the%20students%20were%20planning%20to%20orchestrate%20large-scale%20violence%20during%20today's%20march%20%26quot%3Band%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20of%20murder%20and%20attempted%20murder%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20Interest%20of%20public%20safety%20and%20security%2C%20and%20their%20families%20have%20been%20informed%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20Mr%20Adhikari%20then%20said%20that%20the%20families%20of%20the%20four%20students%20have%20approached%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20organisers%2C%20Shubankar%20Halder%2C%20has%20said%20he%20used%20to%20be%20an%20ABVP%20member%20at%20one%20point%2C%20but%20is%20not%20linked%20to%20the%20organisation%20anymore.%20He%20said%20this%20protest%20is%20an%20apolitical%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20has%20said%20this%20march%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20chaos%20in%20the%20name%20of%20students'%20protest.%20State%20minister%20Chandrima%20Bhattacharya%20told%20the%20media%20yesterday%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20BJP-ABVP%20plot%20to%20create%20disturbance.%20This%20is%20a%20plot%20to%20open%20fire%20by%20criminals%20in%20police%20uniform.%20Tomorrow%20there%20are%20exams.%20Can%20students%20do%20this%3F%20They%20are%20doing%20vulture%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20released%20two%20videos%20to%20stress%20that%20there%20is%20a%20plot%20to%20create%20unrest.%20In%20the%20videos%2C%20the%20authenticity%20of%20which%20NDTV%20has%20not%20verified%2C%20several%20men%20are%20heard%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20need%20bodies%26quot%3B.%20Trinamool%20leader%20Jayprakash%20Majumdar%20alleged%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20leadership%20has%20been%20told%20that%20unless%20a%20Nandigram-type%20incident%20happens%20and%20there%20are%20dead%20bodies%2C%20the%20tide%20will%20not%20turn%20in%20BJP's%20favour.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724746800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fa8721o0o_kolkata-protest_625x300_27_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprotesters-throw-stones-break-barricades-cops-use-tear-gas-in-kolkata-6427414%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chaotic%20scenes%20are%20being%20witnessed%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Kolkata%20as%20police%20intercepted%20a%20protest%20march%20to%20state%20secretariat%20Nabanna%20over%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20in%20the%20city's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20on%20August%209.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprotesters-throw-stones-break-barricades-cops-use-tear-gas-in-kolkata-6427414%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAs%20Observed%20With%20Manish%20Sisodia...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Quotes%20In%20K%20Kavitha%20Hearing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20find%20that%20the%20investigation%20is%20complete.%20As%20such%2C%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20appellant%20is%20not%20necessary%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20investigation.%20The%20appellant%20has%20been%20behind%20bars%20for%20the%20last%20five%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20observed%20in%20Manish%20Sisodia's%20case%2C%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20trial%20being%20conducted%20in%20the%20near%20future%20is%20impossible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20said%20in%20various%20pronouncements%20of%20this%20court%2C%20undertrial%20custody%20should%20not%20turn%20into%20a%20punishment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20law%20provides%20special%20treatment%20for%20women%20while%20considering%20bail%20applications.%20Courts%20need%20to%20be%20more%20sensitive%20and%20sympathetic%20to%20those%20in%20that%20category.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOn%20the%20controversial%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20observation%20that%20an%20educated%2C%20sophisticated%20woman%20is%20not%20entitled%20to%20bail%20under%20the%20beneficiary%20provision%20for%20women%20under%20PMLA%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20order%20is%20allowed%20to%20become%20law%20these%20perverse%20observations%20would%20mean%20no%20educated%20woman%20can%20get%20bail.%20It%20would%20apply%20at%20least%20to%20all%20courts%20in%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20Delhi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724746800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Flgcnk0ao_k-kavitha-pti_625x300_20_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-observed-in-manish-sisodia-what-court-said-while-giving-k-kavitha-bail-6427755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20granted%20bail%20to%20Bharat%20Rashtr