eing%20presidential%20against%20an%20ex-President%20variously%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bweird%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3Bunserious%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20their%20minds%26quot%3B-%20a%20characterisation%20that%20seems%20credible%20not%20only%20due%20to%20his%20record%20in%20office%20but%20also%20because%20he%20continues%20to%20display%20these%20traits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20circumstances%20have%20given%20her%20this%20opening%3F%20According%20to%20Annette%20Gordon-Reed%2C%20a%20Harvard%20law%20and%20history%20professor%3A%20%26quot%3BMany%20Americans%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20feel%20good%20and%20positive%20about%20the%20country's%20political%20future%20in%20the%20face%20of%20all%20that%20we%20have%20lived%20through%20this%20past%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20not%20only%20to%20the%20horrific%20days%20of%20COVID%20but%20also%20to%20the%20severe%20inflation%20and%20housing%20prices%20under%20Biden%2C%20which%20have%20convinced%20many%20Americans%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20a%20disaster%20when%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20has%20rarely%20been%20stronger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'For%20All%20Americans'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%26quot%3Bacceptance%26quot%3B%20portion%20of%20her%2038-minute%20speech%2C%20Ms.%20Harris%20captured%20this%20sentiment%20brilliantly%2C%20even%20as%20she%20took%20swipes%20at%20Trump%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20nation%20with%20this%20election%20has%20a%20precious%2C%20fleeting%20opportunity%20to%20move%20past%20the%20bitterness%2C%20cynicism%20and%20divisive%20battles%20of%20the%20past%2C%20a%20chance%20to%20chart%20a%20new%20way%20forward.%20Not%20as%20members%20of%20any%20one%20party%20or%20faction%2C%20but%20as%20Americans...And%20let%20me%20say%2C%20I%20know%20there%20are%20people%20of%20various%20political%20views%20watching%20tonight.%20And%20I%20want%20you%20to%20know%2C%20I%20promise%20to%20be%20a%20president%20for%20all%20Americans.%20You%20can%20always%20trust%20me%20to%20put%20country%20above%20party%20and%20self.%20To%20hold%20sacred%20America's%20fundamental%20principles%2C%20from%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%2C%20to%20the%20peaceful%20transfer%20of%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20be%20a%20president%20who%20unites%20us%20around%20our%20highest%20aspirations.%20A%20president%20who%20leads%20and%20listens%3B%20who%20is%20realistic%2C%20practical%20and%20has%20common%20sense%3B%20and%20always%20fights%20for%20the%20American%20people.%20From%20the%20courthouse%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20that%20has%20been%20my%20life's%20work.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs.%20Harris%20and%20the%20Democrats%20arrived%20at%20the%20convention%20riding%20high%20on%20the%20wave%20of%20%26quot%3BKamalamania%26quot%3B%20since%20Biden%20handed%20over%20the%20baton.%20But%20they%20faced%20three%20formidable%20challenges%20at%20the%20event%3A%20to%20introduce%20Kamala%20Harris%20to%20a%20public%20that%20knew%20little%20about%20her%3B%20to%20shift%20Biden's%20strategy%20from%20portraying%20Trump%20as%20an%20autocrat%20threatening%20democracy%20to%20framing%20him%20as%20something%20small%20yet%20very%20dangerous%3B%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20to%20persuade%20the%20approximately%2010%25%20of%20undecided%20and%20independent%20voters%2C%20in%20an%20otherwise%20almost%20equally%20divided%20electorate%2C%20to%20join%20their%20cause.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20political%20observers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20from%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20agree%20that%20the%20first%20two%20objectives%20were%20achieved%20at%20the%20convention%20with%20notable%20skill.%20However%2C%20the%20jury%20is%20still%20out%20on%20the%20third%20and%20most%20critical%20objective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We%20Are%20Not%20Going%20Back'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs.%20Harris%20began%20her%20address%20by%20introducing%20her%20immigrant%20parents%2C%20but%20every%20reference%20to%20them%20focused%20on%20the%20values%20they%20instilled%20that%20Americans%20hold%20dear.%20From%20her%20father%3A%20be%20fearless.%20From%20her%20mother%3A%20don't%20complain%20about%20injustice%20-%20do%20something%20about%20it.%20Don't%20do%20anything%20half-assed.%20Make%20the%20most%20of%20available%20opportunities%20and%20be%20grateful%20for%20them.%20Never%20let%20anyone%20tell%20you%20who%20you%20are%3B%20show%20them%20who%20you%20are.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20described%20Trump%20as%20%26quot%3Bunserious%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20emphasising%20that%20his%20success%20in%20the%20election%20would%20have%20very%20%26quot%3Bserious%26quot%3B%20consequences.%20Overall%2C%20she%20positioned%20herself%20as%20a%20safer%20bet%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20U.S.%2C%20using%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bforward%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bfuture%26quot%3B%20eight%20times%20in%20her%20speech%20and%20making%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20not%20going%20back%26quot%3B%20(a%20reference%20to%20Trump%20and%20his%20dystopia)%20her%20signature%20phrase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Takedown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20evisceration%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20was%2C%20as%20expected%2C%20a%20collective%20effort%2C%20in%20which%20every%20major%20convention%20speaker%20participated%2C%20notably%2C%20Oprah%20Winfrey%2C%20the%20Clintons%2C%20and%20the%20Obamas.%20However%2C%20nobody%20did%20it%20better%20than%20Michelle%20Obama.%20She%20mentioned%20him%20only%20once%20but%20brought%20the%20house%20down%20with%20this%20line%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20never%20benefit%20from%20the%20affirmative%20action%20of%20generational%20wealth.%26quot%3B%20And%20then%20the%20coup%20de%20gr%C3%A2ce%3A%20%26quot%3BWho%20is%20going%20to%20tell%20him%20that%20the%20job%20he%20is%20currently%20seeking%20may%20be%20one%20of%20those%20Black%20jobs%3F%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20pointed%20reference%20to%20Trump's%20remark%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20Black%20journalists%20that%20immigrants%20were%20taking%20%26quot%3BBlack%20jobs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20their%20own%20experience%2C%20the%20Obamas%20stressed%20that%20the%20election%20would%20be%20very%20close%20and%20urged%20Democrats%20to%20seize%20every%20opportunity%20to%20bolster%20their%20vote.%20MAGA%20supporters%20are%20largely%20drawn%20from%20non-college-educated%20Gen%20X%20men%2C%20rural%20folks%2C%20and%20believers.%20Harris%20can%20reasonably%20hope%20that%20popular%20Minnesota%20Governor%20Tim%20%26quot%3BCoach%26quot%3B%20Walz%2C%20her%20VP%20nominee%2C%20can%20attract%20some%20of%20those%20votes%20in%20the%20three%20Rust%20Belt%20swing%20states%20of%20Michigan%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOprah%20Winfrey%20explicitly%20reached%20out%20to%20independents%20and%20undecided%20voters%2C%20even%20as%20she%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Trump%2C%20saying%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20that%20America%20is%20an%20ongoing%20project%20requiring%20commitment%2C%20values%2C%20character%2C%20decency%2C%20respect%2C%20plain%20common%20sense%20-%20and%20an%20adult%20conversation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Centrist%20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs.%20Harris's%20speech%20notably%20leaned%20toward%20the%20centre%20in%20terms%20of%20policies%20and%20posture%2C%20with%20no%20extravagant%20promises%20on%20healthcare%20or%20the%20economy.%20Some%20observers%20even%20described%20the%20speech%20as%20leaning%20conservative%2C%20particularly%20in%20her%20promise%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20bipartisan%20tough%20border%20bill%20that%20Trump%20had%20torpedoed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20little%20in%20the%20convention%20speeches%20that%20would%20seriously%20challenge%20the%20widespread%20perception%20that%20Trump%20has%20a%20better%20handle%20on%20the%20economy%20or%20prompt%20a%20reconsideration%20among%20core%20MAGA%20supporters.%20Trump%20has%20sharp%20political%20instincts%20and%2C%20as%20a%20firm%20believer%20in%20transactional%20politics%2C%20has%20no%20hesitation%20in%20abandoning%20even%20the%20firmest%20ideological%20positions%20if%20the%20ground%20shifts.%20Seeing%20how%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%20on%20abortion%20rights%20has%20given%20the%20Democrats%20a%20distinct%20lead%20among%20women%20voters%2C%20Trump%20has%20not%20only%20distanced%20himself%20from%20the%20extreme%20MAGA%20position%20of%20advocating%20a%20national%20ban%20on%20abortion%20but%20also%20claimed%20his%20election%20would%20be%20good%20for%20%26quot%3Breproductive%20rights.%26quot%3B%20He%20hasn't%20elaborated%20on%20how%2C%20but%20he%20is%20using%20terminology%20that%20pro-lifers%20abhor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Democrats%20Are%20Hopeful%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hard%20fact%20remains%20that%20Trump%20still%20leads%20Harris%20in%20five%20of%20the%20seven%20swing%20states%20that%20will%20determine%20the%20election.%20However%2C%20Democrats%20draw%20hope%20from%20three%20developments.%20First%2C%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20has%20begun%20to%20stem%20its%20declining%20support%20among%20blue-collar%20Americans%2C%20Blacks%2C%20and%20Hispanics.%20Second%2C%20Harris%20has%20pulled%20ahead%20in%20at%20least%20two%20states%20and%20reduced%20the%20deficit%20in%20the%20other%20five%20where%20Biden%20was%20trailing%20in%20all%20seven.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20unlike%20Hillary%20Clinton%2C%20this%20contender%20is%20not%20underestimating%20Trump.%20Far%20from%20it.%20Knowing%2C%20as%20Obama%20put%20it%2C%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bweird%26quot%3B%20fascination%20with%20crowd%20size%2C%20Harris%20and%20Walz%20campaigned%20in%20Milwaukee%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20where%20the%20Republicans%20had%20held%20their%20%26quot%3BVictory%20is%20Ours%26quot%3B%20convention%20in%20June%2C%20on%20Day%202%20of%20the%20Democratic%20convention.%20And%20they%20chose%20the%20same%20venue%20and%20drew%20a%20similarly%20large%20and%20enthusiastic%20crowd.%20And%20you%20can%20be%20sure%20that%2C%20unlike%20Clinton%2C%20Harris%20and%20Walz%20will%20aggressively%20campaign%20in%20the%20swing%20states%20in%20the%20remaining%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20November%205%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESomething%20%26quot%3BMagical%26quot%3B%20In%20The%20Air%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20dubbed%20this%20period%20as%20Harris'%20%26quot%3Bhoneymoon%26quot%3B%20and%20correctly%20predict%20tough%20days%20ahead%20for%20her.%20Her%20performance%20against%20Trump%20in%20the%20debate%20on%20September%2010%20will%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20undecided%20and%20independent%20voters.%20The%20U.S.%20media%20is%20eager%20to%20scrutinise%20her%20when%20she%20gives%20her%20first%20press%20conference%20or%20detailed%20interview%20as%20the%20Democratic%20nominee.%20Her%20bid%20for%20the%20party%20nomination%20in%202020%20was%20effectively%20derailed%20by%20a%20disastrous%20press%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Democrats%20were%20in%20deep%20despair%20after%20Biden's%20poor%20performance%20in%20the%20debate%20with%20Trump%20in%20late%20June.%20They%20could%20not%20have%20known%20that%20this%20disaster%20would%20be%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20happen%20to%20them%3A%20it%20pushed%20Biden%20out%20and%2C%20unexpectedly%20for%20Trump%2C%20brought%20in%20Kamala%2C%20who%20came%20out%20swinging%20and%20surprised%20everyone%20with%20her%20style%20and%20savvy.%20Today%2C%20when%20Michelle%20Obama%20says%20there%20is%20something%20%26quot%3Bmagical%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20air%2C%20even%20Republicans%20are%20beginning%20to%20acknowledge%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Republican%20strategist%20Mark%20Mackinnon%20put%20it%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20feels%20like%20something%20completely%20different%20is%20happening.%20And%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20it%20is%20yet%2C%20but%2C%20you%20know%2C%20just%20the%20circumstances%2C%20the%20timing%2C%20the%20compressed%20election%2C%20the%20nomination%