gi%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20ED's%20%26quot%3Bbogus%26quot%3B%20claim%26quot%3B%2C%20arguing%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20you%20say%20I%20'destroyed'%20my%20phone...%20people%20change%20phones.%20I%20changed%20my%20phone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-liquor-policy-scam-k-kavitha-destroyed-9-phones-stayed-in-rs-10-lakh-hotel-room-probe-agency-5807709%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EK%20Kavitha%20Destroyed%209%20Phones%3A%20Probe%20Agency%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%2C%20though%2C%20questioned%20Ms%20Kavitha's%20actions%2C%20counter-arguing%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20would%20you%20give%20a%20maid%20or%20a%20servant%20an%20iPhone%20(authorities%20had%20earlier%20said%20the%20BRS%20leader%20gave%20one%20of%20the%20reformatted%20phones%20to%20her%20maid)...%20her%20conduct%20amounts%20to%20tampering%20(with%20evidence).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20also%20questioned%20how%20a%20phone%20used%20by%20a%20senior%20political%20leader%20for%20at%20least%20four%20months%20could%20contain%20no%20messages.%20%26quot%3BOn%20examination%20of%20the%20phone%20it%20is%20found%20there%20is%20no%20data%20(but)%20you%20have%20been%20using%20the%20phone%20for%20four%20to%20six%20months%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20though%2C%20was%20unconvinced%2C%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20delete%20messages%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20deleting%20messages...%20normal%20conduct.%20Any%20of%20us%20in%20this%20room%20(do%20it)%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20KV%20Viswanathan%20said%2C%20but%20the%20prosecution%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20do%20not%20delete%20contacts%2C%20history...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724744520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fp9qbt85_k-kavitha-rouse-avenue-court_625x300_05_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%