oiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112829933%2Cimgsize-660857.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fis-god-real-controversial-high-school-assignment-sparks-online-debate-netizens-react%2Farticleshow%2F112827967.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20high%20school%20assignment%20in%20Oklahoma%20questioning%20the%20existence%20of%20God%20and%20Satan%20provoked%20a%20viral%20backlash%20after%20a%20parent%20posted%20it%20on%20Facebook.%20Skiatook%20Public%20Schools%20responded%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20assignment%20did%20not%20align%20with%20their%20instructional%20plan%2C%20and%20promised%20improvements%20while%20addressing%20public%20concerns%20about%20religious%20bias%20in%20public%20education.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fis-god-real-controversial-high-school-assignment-sparks-online-debate-netizens-react%2Farticleshow%2F112827967.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Mpox%20Strain%20Mutating%20Very%20Rapidly.%20How%20Scientists%20Are%20Responding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EScientists%20studying%20the%20new%20mpox%20strain%20that%20has%20spread%20out%20of%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%20say%20the%20virus%20is%20changing%20faster%20than%20expected%20and%20often%20in%20areas%20where%20experts%20lack%20the%20funding%20and%20equipment%20to%20properly%20track%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20there%20are%20multiple%20unknowns%20about%20the%20virus%20itself%2C%20its%20severity%20and%20how%20it%20is%20transmitting%2C%20complicating%20the%20response%2C%20half%20a%20dozen%20scientists%20in%20Africa%2C%20Europe%20and%20the%20United%20States%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMpox%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20monkeypox%2C%20has%20been%20a%20public%20health%20problem%20in%20parts%20of%20Africa%20since%201970%2C%20but%20received%20little%20global%20attention%20until%20it%20surged%20internationally%20in%202022%2C%20prompting%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20to%20declare%20a%20global%20health%20emergency.%20That%20declaration%20ended%2010%20months%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20strain%20of%20the%20virus%2C%20known%20as%20clade%20Ib%2C%20has%20the%20world's%20attention%20again%20after%20the%20WHO%20declared%20a%20new%20health%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strain%20is%20a%20mutated%20version%20of%20clade%20I%2C%20a%20form%20of%20mpox%20spread%20by%20contact%20with%20infected%20animals%20that%20has%20been%20endemic%20in%20Congo%20for%20decades.%20Mpox%20typically%20causes%20flu-like%20symptoms%20and%20pus-filled%20lesions%20and%20can%20kill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongo%20has%20had%20more%20than%2018%2C000%20suspected%20clade%20I%20and%20clade%20Ib%20mpox%20cases%20and%20615%20deaths%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20WHO.%20There%20have%20also%20been%20222%20confirmed%20clade%20Ib%20cases%20in%20four%20African%20countries%20in%20the%20last%20month%2C%20plus%20a%20case%20each%20in%20Sweden%20and%20Thailand%20in%20people%20with%20a%20travel%20history%20in%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20worry%20that%20in%20Africa%2C%20we%20are%20working%20blindly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr.%20Dimie%20Ogoina%2C%20an%20infectious%20diseases%20expert%20at%20Niger%20Delta%20University%20Hospital%20in%20Nigeria%20who%20chairs%20the%20WHO's%20mpox%20emergency%20committee.%20He%20first%20raised%20the%20alarm%20about%20potential%20sexual%20transmission%20of%20mpox%20in%202017%2C%20now%20an%20accepted%20route%20of%20spread%20for%20the%20virus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20understand%20our%20outbreak%20very%20well%2C%20and%20if%20we%20don't%20understand%20our%20outbreak%20very%20well%20we%20will%20have%20difficulty%20addressing%20the%20problem%20in%20terms%20of%20transmission%20dynamics%2C%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20disease%2C%20risk%20factors%20of%20the%20disease%2C%26quot%3B%20Ogoina%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20worry%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20virus%20seems%20to%20be%20mutating%20and%20producing%20new%20strains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20took%20clade%20IIb%20in%20Nigeria%20five%20years%20or%20more%20to%20evolve%20enough%20for%20sustained%20spread%20among%20humans%2C%20sparking%20the%202022%20global%20outbreak.%20Clade%20Ib%20has%20done%20the%20same%20thing%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMUTATING%20'MORE%20RAPIDLY'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMpox%20is%20an%20orthopoxvirus%2C%20the%20same%20family%20that%20causes%20smallpox.%20Population-wide%20protection%20from%20a%20global%20vaccine%20campaign%2050%20years%20ago%20has%20waned%2C%20as%20the%20vaccinating%20stopped%20when%20the%20disease%20was%20eradicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenetic%20sequencing%20of%20clade%20Ib%20infections%2C%20which%20the%20WHO%20estimates%20emerged%20mid-September%202023%2C%20show%20they%20carry%20a%20mutation%20known%20as%20APOBEC3%2C%20a%20signature%20of%20adaptation%20in%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virus%20that%20causes%20mpox%20has%20typically%20been%20fairly%20stable%20and%20slow%20to%20mutate%2C%20but%20APOBEC-driven%20mutations%20can%20accelerate%20viral%20evolution%2C%20said%20Dr.%20Miguel%20Paredes%2C%20who%20is%20studying%20the%20evolution%20of%20mpox%20and%20other%20viruses%20at%20Fred%20Hutchison%20Cancer%20Center%20in%20Seattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20human-to-human%20cases%20of%20mpox%20have%20this%20APOBEC%20signature%20of%20mutations%2C%20which%20means%20that%20it's%20mutating%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20rapidly%20than%20we%20would%20expect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParedes%20and%20other%20scientists%20said%20a%20response%20was%20complicated%20by%20several%20mpox%20outbreaks%20happening%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20mpox%20was%20predominantly%20acquired%20through%20human%20contact%20with%20infected%20animals.%20That%20is%20still%20driving%20a%20rise%20in%20Congo%20in%20clade%20I%20cases%20-%20also%20known%20as%20clade%20Ia%20-%20likely%20due%20in%20part%20to%20deforestation%20and%20increased%20consumption%20of%20bushmeat%2C%20scientists%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mutated%20versions%2C%20clade%20Ib%20and%20IIb%2C%20can%20now%20essentially%20be%20considered%20a%20sexually%20transmitted%20disease%2C%20said%20Dr.%20Salim%20Abdool%20Karim%2C%20a%20South%20African%20epidemiologist%20and%20chair%20of%20the%20Africa%20CDC's%20mpox%20advisory%20committee.%20Most%20of%20the%20mutated%20clade%20Ib%20cases%20are%20among%20adults%2C%20driven%20at%20first%20by%20an%20epidemic%20among%20female%20sex%20workers%20in%20South%20Kivu%2C%20Congo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virus%20also%20can%20spread%20through%20close%20contact%20with%20an%20infected%20person%2C%20which%20is%20likely%20how%20clusters%20of%20children%20have%20been%20infected%20with%20clade%20Ib%2C%20particularly%20in%20Burundi%20and%20in%20eastern%20Congo's%20displacement%20camps%2C%20where%20crowded%20living%20conditions%20may%20be%20contributing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChildren%2C%20pregnant%20women%20and%20people%20with%20weakened%20immune%20systems%20may%20be%20at%20greater%20risk%20of%20serious%20mpox%20disease%20and%20death%2C%20according%20to%20the%20WHO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClade%20I%20has%20typically%20caused%20more%20severe%20disease%2C%20with%20fatality%20rates%20of%204%25-11%25%2C%20compared%20to%20around%201%25%20for%20clade%20II.%20Ogoina%20said%20data%20from%20Congo%20suggests%20few%20have%20died%20of%20the%20new%20Ib%20version%2C%20but%20he%20feared%20some%20data%20is%20being%20mixed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20research%20is%20urgently%20needed%2C%20but%20three%20teams%20tracking%20mpox%20outbreaks%20in%20Africa%20say%20they%20cannot%20even%20access%20chemicals%20needed%20for%20diagnostic%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlanning%20a%20response%2C%20including%20vaccination%20strategies%2C%20without%20this%20is%20difficult%2C%20the%20scientists%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarim%20said%20around%20half%20of%20cases%20in%20eastern%20Congo%2C%20where%20Ib%20is%20particularly%20prevalent%2C%20are%20only%20being%20diagnosed%20by%20doctors%2C%20with%20no%20laboratory%20confirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20samples%20to%20labs%20is%20difficult%20because%20the%20healthcare%20system%20is%20already%20under%20pressure%2C%20he%20said.%20And%20around%20750%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20amid%20fighting%20between%20the%20M23%20rebel%20group%20and%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20African%20laboratories%20cannot%20get%20the%20supplies%20they%20need%2C%20said%20Dr.%20Emmanuel%20Nakoune%2C%20an%20mpox%20expert%20at%20the%20Institut%20Pasteur%20in%20Bangui%2C%20Central%20African%20Republic%2C%20which%20also%20has%20clade%20Ia%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20luxury%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20but%20necessary%20to%20track%20deadly%20outbreaks.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724742720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fdake6ch_mpox-monkeypox-health-emergency_625x300_27_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-mpox-strain-mutating-very-rapidly-how-scientists-are-responding-6426881%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20studying%20the%20new%20mpox%20strain%20that%20has%20spread%20out%20of%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%20say%20the%20virus%20is%20changing%20faster%20than%20expected%20and%20often%20in%20areas%20where%20experts%20lack%20the%20funding%20and%20equipment%20to%20properly%20track%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-mpox-strain-mutating-very-rapidly-how-scientists-are-responding-6426881%22%2C%22cdnA