20Okha%20%26amp%3B%20Dwarka%20-7each%2C%20Porbandar-5%2C%26quot%3B%20IMD%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vishwamitri%20river%20that%20flows%20through%20Vadodara%20has%20been%20overflowing%20leading%20to%20residential%20areas%20experiencing%20severe%20waterlogging.%20People%20were%20seen%20wading%20through%20knee-deep%20waters%20and%20the%20waterlogging%20led%20to%20traffic%20snarls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20heavy%20rainfall%2C%20water%20from%20Ajwa%20Reservoir%20and%20Pratappura%20Reservoir%20was%20released%20into%20Vishwamitri%20River%2C%20leading%20to%20waterlogging%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20said%20that%20severe%20waterlogging%20had%20been%20experienced%20since%20Monday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWater%20has%20entered%20houses%20since%20Monday%20evening%20in%20low-lying%20areas.%20People%20are%20shifting%20to%20other%20safe%20locations.%20There%20is%20a%20shortage%20of%20food.%20People%20are%20facing%20a%20lot%20of%20difficulty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResident%20said%20that%20they%20had%20never%20seen%20a%20flood-like%20situation%20like%20this%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Mahadev%20Temple%20complex%20in%20Vadodara%20was%20submerged%20due%20to%20heavy%20rainfall%20and%20the%20temple%20premises%20were%20shut%20on%20Tuesday.%20People%20said%20that%20they%20had%20never%20seen%20this%20much%20rain%20in%20the%20last%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gandhinagar%20number%20plates%20of%20vehicles%20were%20found%20scattered%20at%20Mahatma%20Mandir%20Underbridge%2C%20Sector-13%20after%20the%20water%20receded.%20The%20area%20faced%20severe%20waterlogging%20due%20to%20incessant%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChief%20Minister%20Bhupendra%20Patel%20has%20held%20a%20meeting%20today%20with%20all%20the%20district%20officials%20through%20videoconference%20and%20directed%20us%20regarding%20human%20life.%20He%20dir