US%20politician%20saw%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20indulge%20in%20what%20his%20daughter%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpeculiar%20fascination%20with%20dead%20animals%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20a%20chainsaw%2C%20RFK%20Jr%20reportedly%20hurried%20down%20to%20the%20beach%20and%20proceeded%20to%20decapitate%20the%20whale%20on%20the%20spot.%20He%20then%20attached%20the%20massive%20head%20to%20the%20family's%20minivan%20with%20a%20bungee%20cord%2C%20determined%20to%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20their%20home%20in%20Mount%20Kisco%2C%20New%20York%2C%20for%20further%20study.%20The%20family%20endured%20a%20five-hour%20drive%20back%2C%20with%20the%20whale's%20rotting%20remains%20emitting%20a%20stench%20that%2C%20according%20to%20Kick%20Kennedy%2C%20assaulted%20every%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20we%20accelerated%20on%20the%20highway%2C%20whale%20juice%20would%20pour%20into%20the%20windows%20of%20the%20car%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20rankest%20thing%20on%20the%20planet%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Kennedy%C2%A0recalled%20in%20the%20interview.%20The%20situation%20was%20so%20unbearable%20that%20the%20family%20resorted%20to%20wearing%20plastic%20bags%20over%20their%20heads%20with%20mouth%20holes%20cut%20out%2C%20which%20brought%20out%20bewildered%20and%20disgusted%20reactions%20from%20fellow%20drivers.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20on%20the%20highway%20were%20giving%20us%20the%20finger%2C%20but%20that%20was%20just%20normal%20day-to-day%20stuff%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20she%C2%A0revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20whale%20beheading%20incident%20is%20disturbing%2C%20it%20was%20not%20the%20only%20such%20occurrence%20in%20the%20Kennedy%20household.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20RFK%20Jr%20admitted%20in%20a%20viral%20interview%20with%20Roseanne%20Barr%20that%20he%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F08%2F04%2Fus-news%2Frfk-jr-says-he-dumped-dead-bear-in-central-park-after-ditching-plan-to-skin-it-in-bizarre-video%2F%5C%22%3Edumped%20a%20dead%20bear%20cub%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Central%20Park%20a%20decade%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recounted%20how%2C%20during%20a%20falconing%20trip%20in%20Goshen%2C%20New%20York%2C%20he%20discovered%20the%20cub%20after%20it%20had%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20car.%20Planning%20to%20skin%20the%20bear%20and%20use%20the%20meat%2C%20he%20placed%20it%20in%20his%20van.%20However%2C%20after%20a%20night%20of%20drinking%20with%20friends%2C%20they%20decided%20it%20would%20be%20amusing%20to%20dump%20the%20bear%20in%20Central%20Park%20and%20make%20it%20appear%20as%20though%20it%20had%20been%20hit%20by%20a%20bike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20these%20bizarre%20stories%20resurface%2C%20the%20spotlight%20is%20also%20on%20Ms%20Kennedy%2C%20who%20has%20recently%20been%20seen%20in%20the%20company%20of%20recently%20divorced%20Ben%20Affleck%2C%2052.%20The%20two%20have%20been%20spotted%20at%20various%20hotspots%2C%20including%20the%20Polo%20Lounge%20at%20the%20Beverly%20Hills%20Hotel%2C%20leading%20to%20dating%20rumours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724739600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqnku3nn_kick-kennedy_625x300_27_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgruesome-whale-story-involving-rfk-jr-resurfaces-as-kick-kennedy-spends-time-with-ben-affleck-6426742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bizarre%20tale%20involving%20Robert%20Francis%20Kennedy%20Jr%20has%20resurfaced.%20The%20story%2C%20first%20shared%20by%20Kick%20Kennedy%20--%20the%20daughter%20of%20RFK%20Jr%20--%20witha%20magazine%2C%20sheds%20light%20on%20a%20childhood%20memory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgruesome-whale-story-involving-rfk-jr-resurfaces-as-kick-kennedy-spends-time-with-ben-affleck-6426742%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientist%20Claims%20He's%20Found%20%26quot%3BPerfect%20Hiding%20Place%26quot%3B%20For%20Missing%20MH370%20Flight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYears%20after%20its%20disappearance%2C%20an%20Australian%20scientist%20has%20claimed%20that%20he%20has%20found%20the%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20hiding%20place%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20missing%20MH370%20plane.%20The%20Malaysian%20Airlines%20flight%2C%20with%20239%20people%20on%20board%2C%20vanished%20from%20radar%20after%20taking%20off%20from%20Kuala%20Lumpur%20in%202014.%20Its%20disappearance%20sparked%20the%20biggest%20search%20in%20aviation%20history%20with%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20the%20jet%20still%20unknown%20to%20this%20day.%20Now%2C%20Tasmanian%20researcher%20Vincent%20Lyne%20has%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20he%20has%20figured%20out%20where%20the%20plane%20is.%20In%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%2C%20Mr%20Lyne%20claimed%20that%20the%20plane%20was%20deliberately%20ploughed%20deep%20into%20the%20Broken%20Ridge%20-%20a%2020%2C000-foot-deep%20hole%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20work%20changes%20the%20narrative%20of%20MH370's%20disappearance%20from%20one%20of%20no-blame%2C%20fuel-starvation%20at%20the%207th%20arc%2C%20high-speed%20dive%2C%20to%20a%20mastermind%20pilot%20almost%20executing%20an%20incredible%20perfect-disappearance%20in%20the%20Southern%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20researcher%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20it%20would%20have%20worked%20were%20it%20not%20for%20MH370%20ploughing%20its%20right%20wing%20through%20a%20wave%2C%20and%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20regular%20interrogation%20satellite%20communications%20by%20Inmarsat%20-%20a%20brilliant%20discovery%20also%20announced%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Navigation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3AugcPost%3A7231166380627148800%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22501%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lyne%2C%20who%20works%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Tasmania's%20Institute%20for%20Marine%20and%20Antarctic%20Studies%2C%20further%20said%20that%20damage%20to%20the%20plane's%20wings%2C%20flaps%20and%20flaperon%20suggest%20it%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bcontrolled%20ditching%26quot%3B%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20Captain%20Chesley%20%26quot%3BSully%26quot%3B%20Sullenberger%20on%20the%20Hudson%20River%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20justifies%20beyond%20doubt%20the%20original%20claim%2C%20based%20on%20brilliant%2C%20skilled%2C%20and%20very%20careful%20debris-damage%20analyses%2C%20by%20decorated%20ex-Chief%20Canadian%20Air-crash%20Investigator%20Larry%20Vance%2C%20that%20MH370%20had%20fuel%20and%20running%20engines%20when%20it%20underwent%20a%20masterful%20'controlled%20ditching'%20and%20not%20a%20high-speed%20fuel-starved%20crash%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lyne%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20researcher%20stated%20that%20MH370%20is%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20longitude%20of%20Penang%20airport%20(the%20runway%20no%20less)%20intersects%20the%20Pilot-in-Command%20home%20simulator%20track%20discovered%20and%20discarded%20by%20the%20FBI%20and%20officials%20as%20'irrelevant.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmysterious-woman-linked-to-arrest-of-telegram-ceo-called-mossad-agent-all-about-juli-vavilova-6420329%5C%22%3EMysterious%20Woman%20Linked%20To%20Arrest%20Of%20Telegram%20CEO%2C%20Called%20Mossad%20Agent%3A%20All%20About%20Juli%20Vavilova%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20pre-meditated%20iconic%20location%20harbors%20a%20very%20deep%206000m%20hole%20at%20the%20eastern%20end%20of%20the%20Broken%20Ridge%20within%20a%20very%20rugged%20and%20dangerous%20ocean%20environment%20renowned%20for%20its%20wild%20fisheries%20and%20new%20deep-water%20species.%20With%20narrow%20steep%20sides%2C%20sur