%20forest%20in%20the%20once%20barren%20land.%20There%20are%20now%20over%20500%20trees.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-10-1724336056.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Medini%20Homestay%20is%20a%20green%20oasis%20where%20fruit%2C%20herb%20and%20vegetable%20trees%20thrive%20together%20in%20a%20single%20space%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-10-1724336056.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-10-1724336056-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-10-1724336056-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-10-1724336056-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-10-1724336056-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362636%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMedini%20Homestay%20is%20a%20green%20oasis%20where%20fruit%2C%20herb%20and%20vegetable%20trees%20thrive%20together%20in%20a%20single%20space.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20took%20on%20the%20challenge%20head-on.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20land%20had%20been%20excavated%20in%20parts%2C%20thus%20lacking%20a%20topsoil%20layer.%20When%20I%20began%20work%20on%20the%20land%2C%20there%20were%20around%20three%20trees%20and%20a%20small%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356551%2Fbest-tea-plantation-estates-homestays-legacy-heritage-india-assam-tamil-nadu-darjeeling%2F%5C%22%20tar