F281446%2Fiit-innovation-engineer-builds-biogas-plant-organic-matter-cuts-lpg-cost%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustom-built%20biodigester%20plant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20an%20anaerobic%20bacteria%20digester%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20Deka%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-13_11zon-1724336325.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Assamese%20culture%20is%20reflected%20through%20events%20at%20the%20homestay%20and%20the%20food%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-13_11zon-1724336325.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-13_11zon-1724336325-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-13_11zon-1724336325-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-13_11zon-1724336325-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fkaziranga-homestay-13_11zon-1724336325-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Assamese%20culture%20is%20reflected%20through%20events%20at%20the%20homestay%20and%20the%20food.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20grey%20water%20from%20the%20kitchens%20is%20treated%20through%20a%20natural%20reed%20bed%20made%20with%20stones%2C%20sand%2C%20and%20a%20natural%20reed%20bed%2C%20which%20purifies%20the%20water%20before%20it%20returns%20to%20the%20natural%20groundwater.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20amazing%20the%20oasis%20of%20green%20choices%20that