-invents-device-for-dementia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoth%20grandmothers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20their%20age%20and%20health%20conditions%2C%20face%20an%20increased%20risk%20of%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Class%2012%20students%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20passionate%20about%20robotics%2C%20electronics%2C%20and%20coding%2C%20applied%20their%20knowledge%20to%20develop%20an%20innovative%20walking%20stick%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20falls%20%E2%80%94%20a%20common%20concern%20among%20the%20elderly%20and%20those%20with%20conditions%20like%20osteoporosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20kept%20brainstorming%20and%20found%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20their%20solution%20to%20life%20during%20a%20STEM%20competition%20in%202022.%20They%20asked%20themselves%3A%20%E2%80%9CCould%20we%20create%20a%20preventative%20tool%20that%20would%20anticipate%20the%20risk%20of%20falls%20and%20alert%20caregivers%20in%20time%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20two%20years%2C%20the%2018-year-olds%20dedicated%20themselves%20to%20developing%20Walkfit%20%E2%80%94%20a%20system%20that%20attaches%20to%20a%20walking%20stick%20to%20assist%20with%20gait%20analysis%20and%20diagnose%20lower%20limb%20orthopaedic%20disorders.%20The%20teenagers%20utilised%20robotics%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%2C%20and%20machine%20learning%20(ML)%20skills%20they%20honed%20at%20Omotec%20(On%20My%20Own%20Technology).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahi%20and%20Hriday%20have%20won%20many%20accolades%2C%20emerging%20as%20runner-ups%20at%20the%20IIT%20Bombay%20Techfest%20and%20securing%20a%20provisional%20patent%20for%20their%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20Walkfit%20can%20help%20elders%20with%20mobility%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Lego%20to%20real%20robots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahi%20and%20Hriday%E2%80%99s%20interest%20in%20robotics%20received%20a%20fillip%20when%20their%20school%2C%20Podar%20International%