ame%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FnlXbceBCGtY%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20analysing%20pressure%20values%2C%20we%20assess%20how%20dependent%20the%20user%20is%20on%20the%20stick.%20A%20high%20level%20of%20dependence%20indicates%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20falling.%20We%20measure%20how%20much%20of%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20weight%20is%20being%20supported%20by%20the%20stick%3B%20based%20on%20that%2C%20we%20predict%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20fall%20and%20help%20diagnose%20potential%20problems%20or%20underlying%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rahi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circuit%2C%20equipped%20with%20Bluetooth%20modules%2C%20transmits%20data%20to%20a%20laptop%2C%20generating%20real-time%20heat%20maps.%20These%20heat%20maps%20actually%20show%20which%20pressure%20points%20on%20the%20stick%20are%20bearing%20the%20most%20weight%2C%20giving%20an%20insight%20into%20what%20the%20problem%20could%20be%2C%20or%20what%20the%20chances%20of%20fall%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20heat%20maps%20visually%20represent%20pressure%20points%2C%20with%20blue%20indicating%20low%20pressure%20and%20red%20indicating%20high%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%2C%20the%20students%20say%20that%20if%20the%20map%20shows%20high%20pressure%20on%20the%20left%20side%2C%20there%20is%20a%20probability%20that%20the%20user%20has%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20right%20knee%20or%20ankle.%20%E2%80%9CGenerally%2C%20when%20you%20have%20a%20problem%2C%20you%20tend%20to%20put%20less%20weight%20on%20that%20area%2C%20so%20that%20it%20pains%20less.%20You%20tilt%20more%20towards%20the%20opposite%20side%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20left%20side%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20highest%20pressure%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20explain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20plan%20to%20develop%20a%20mobile%20app%20in%20the%20future%20to%20make%20this%20data%20more%20accessible%20to%20users.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20elders%20have%20lower%20body%20issues%20like%20osteoarthritis%2C%20osteoporosis%2C%20buckling%20knees%2C%20and%20hip%20fractures.%20Our%20device%20can%20predict%20falls%20in%20both%20standing%20and%20sitting%20positions.%20It%20detects%20stability%20in%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20gait%20and%20changes%20in%20balance%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Hriday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20641px)%20100vw%2C%20641px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-21-at-18.55.14-1724247056.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20circuit%20attaches%20to%20any%20walking%20stick%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-21-at-18.55.14-1724247056.jpeg%20641w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-21-at-18.55.14-1724247056-267x300.jpeg%20267w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-21-at-18.55.14-1724247056-500x562.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-21-at-18.55.14-1724247056-150x168.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362430%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20circuit%20attaches%20to%20any%20walking%20stick%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20values%20from%20the%20Force%20Sensitive%20Resistors%20(FSR)%20and%20gyro%20sensors%20generate%20a%20heat%20map%2C%20which%20uses%20the%20weight-bearing%20tendencies%20of%20a%20user%20which%20differs%20according%20to%20age%20and%20illness.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20attached%20circuit%20gives%20data%20to%20measure%20movement.%20It%20reads%20the%20amount%20of%20pressure%20due%20to%20weight-bearing%20capacity%20and%20discretional%20tilt%20based%20on%20personal%20parameters%20already%20entered.%20Based%20on%20this%20information%2C%20the%20device%20gives%20an%20early%20signal%20to%20prevent%20falls%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Reetu%20Jain%2C%20chief-mentor%20and%20founder%20of%20Omotec.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20now%20hope%20to%20fine-tune%20their%20invention%20and%20connect%20the%20device%20to%20an%20app.%20In%20a%20day%20and%20age%20when%20most%20seniors%20stay%20alone%2C%20it%20would%20be%20useful%20to%20alert%20their%20children%20or%20caregivers%20who%20stay%20far%20away%20by%20detecting%20problems%20early.%20It%20also%20has%20uses%20for%20doctors%20to%20monitor%20patients%20with%20known%20mobility%20issues.%20The%20device%20can%20monitor%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20condition%2C%20providing%20insights%20into%20their%20risk%20of%20falling%20and%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20their%20current%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahi%20and%20Hriday%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343321%2Frahul-arepaka-harvested-robotics-hyderabad-ai-startup-laser-weeder-robot-help-farmers-earn-more%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etested%20the%20prototype%20on%20their%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20post%20which%20they%20tested%20it%20on%2050%20senior%20citizens%20living%20in%20old%20age%20homes.%20The%20physiotherapists%20validated%20their%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20efforts%20have%20not%20gone%20unnoticed%20%E2%80%94%20they%20qualified%20for%20the%20the%20IIT%20Tech%20Fest%2C%20IRIS%20National%20Fair%2C%20and%20the%20World%