in%20a%20controlled%20environment%20with%20artificial%20light%20without%20depending%20on%20the%20weather%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Calvin%20points%20out%20that%20while%20groundwater%20is%20already%20depleting%20to%20severe%20levels%20and%20agricultural%20lands%20are%20decreasing%2C%20demand%20for%20food%20continues%20to%20increase.%20%E2%80%9CClimate%20change%20is%20rapid%20and%20crop%20loss%20will%20be%20substantial%20due%20to%20this.%20We%20understood%20that%20innovation%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment%20is%20crucial%20and%20AI%20will%20help%20us%20further%20our%20sustainable%20goals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20weekend%2C%20Calvin%20and%20Farish%20spoke%20in%20detail%20on%20the%20persistent%20issue.%20With%20a%20shared%20passion%20for%20transforming%20the%20agricultural%20sector%20through%20technology-driven%20solutions%2C%20they%20eventually%20decided%20to%20completely%20shift%20their%20focus%20on%20making%20farming%20profitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Calvin%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20both%20friends%20rented%20a%20small%20flat%20in%20Udupi%20where%20they%20built%20a%20prototype%20using%20their%20pocket%20money.%20After%20four%20months%2C%20they%20started%20their%20company%2C%20Krop%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECutting%20operational%20costs%20to%20half%20with%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20offering%20container%20farm%20setups%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20polyhouse%20farming%2C%20Calvin%20and%20Farish%20aimed%20to%20boost%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20and%20resilience%20against%20climate%20fluctuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FKrop-AI-1-1723817326.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%