%E2%80%99%20from%20Dover.%20In%20a%20boat%20following%20her%20were%20two%20pilots%2C%20an%20observer%20from%20the%20Channel%20Swimming%20Association%2C%20her%20coach%2C%20husband%2C%20and%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20father%20who%20was%20unwilling%20to%20let%20his%20daughter%20take%20such%20a%20big%20risk%20was%20now%20her%20biggest%20cheerleader.%20At%2064%2C%20he%20had%20to%20wage%20a%20battle%20to%20be%20allowed%20on%20the%20boat.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20usually%20don%E2%80%99t%20allow%20people%20above%2060%20on%20the%20boat%20as%20there%20is%20a%20chance%20of%20sea%20sickness.%20I%20had%20to%20be%20there%20for%20Tanvi%20and%20had%20only%20juices%20for%20two%20days%20before%20and%20carried%20medicines%20to%20prevent%20vomiting%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kiran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9zlIvVu6_M%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9zlIvVu6_M%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9zlIvVu6_M%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20targe